data.description: This classic Rountrey home is ready for the pickiest of buyers. The main level offers a dramatic 2 story family room & open concept for living, kitchen & dining. The kitchen boasts ample cabinets, tons of countertop space & an island. There is a flex space off of kitchen (current exercise room). Oversized pantry & a drop zone off of kitchen. The first-floor office (5th possible bedroom) adds a practical touch with a full bath. Retreat to the master suite for some quiet time with the luxury bath attached.  2nd bedroom has an on-suite, 3rd and 4th bedroom have walk-in closets and share a hall bath. Laundry room is accessible from master closet & hallway. 3rd floor attic is plumbed for bath & would make a great bonus room. The attached 2 car garage, rear deck, huge front & back yard with full irrigation system, front porch, fenced rear yard provide so much space for outside fun. This home is clean and cared for and ready for a new owner. Internet cable in each room & an alarm system. Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of functionality and charm in Rountrey. This community offers a club house, pool and a sense of community with fun activities planned year round.
